maya package manager.
=====================

the use of maya is initially NOT RECOMMENDED, as it is in the early stages of development, and important decisions are still being made.

currently functional packages:
------------------------------

pfetch, neofetch, discord, vault

minimum requirements:
---------------------

   core-utils, base-devel, tar

installation:
-------------

   $ git clone https://github.com/sakaki91/maya $HOME/.local/share/maya
   $ mkdir -p $HOME/.local/bin && ln -sf $HOME/.local/share/maya/maya $HOME/.local/bin
